{"tid":780771,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【玩Kiki challenge惹禍】準港姐陳苑澄愁爆現身 喊住致歉","createTime":"2018-08-15T11:39:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T13:50:26.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"11b016691bb80eec45dcdc056a222971a42ce046","tid":780771,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T11:39:29.000Z","msg":"陳苑澄在社交平台上載Kiki challenge片段，結果惹來負評，今日她喊爆回應。<br />\n<br />\n全片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100003797124298/posts/1328465670623324/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100003797124298%2Fposts%2F1328465670623324%2F&d=FMTmREmLMwwt0A%2F8c0IlfXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=6c517e4f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100003797124298/posts/1328465670623324/</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20180815/s00009/600195b7d97d38a1751425994d499937.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20180815%2Fs00009%2F600195b7d97d38a1751425994d499937.jpg&h=9688b4df&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n應屆候選港姐兼前組合As One成員陳苑澄，前天在社交平台，上載一條挑戰kiki challenge的落車跳舞熱潮短片，結果惹來負評，不少網民留言指她此行為危險，亦有網民指她亂丟垃圾，雖然負評不絕，但陳苑澄仍未刪除該片段。<br />\n<br />\n今天陳苑澄出席港姐活動時，顯得憂心忡忡，笑容欠奉。受訪時，陳苑澄還含淚兼六度鞠躬，為自己輕率行為致歉，懇求公司和公眾原諒。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20180815/s00009/5fe422d70d5c2bd5abe848a0ff99876c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20180815%2Fs00009%2F5fe422d70d5c2bd5abe848a0ff99876c.jpg&h=1202d9ae&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n香港小姐競選大會已向候選佳麗15號陳苑澄了解事件，並告誡其行為可能違反道路交通條例、妄顧自身及其他人仕之安全，往後要多加注意。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ol.mingpao.com/php/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1534320863194&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20180815\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fphp%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1534320863194%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20180815&d=FMTmREmLMwwt0A%2F8c0IlfXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=83d496a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fphp%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1534320863194%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20180815&h=317b9dae\" target=\"_blank\">https://ol.mingpao.com/php/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1534320863194&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20180815</a>"},{"pid":"ec494a42dcffdcb15a87ce7b50d954ba7afef972","tid":780771,"uid":21423,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T11:43:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c576a957c13fbf530354b331d8aff82a200e3fcd","tid":780771,"uid":132587,"like":66,"dislike":1,"score":65,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T11:47:14.000Z","msg":"點解呢個豬西仲會發明星夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aad6992fc91c5b03dbac2d735465598355c6744","tid":780771,"uid":169992,"like":11,"dislike":26,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T11:59:23.000Z","msg":"唔講以為佢揸車撞死咗人<br />\n唔明有嘜好鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b78714519ead39a3ff54ecf7e8dbfb97fbd4462","tid":780771,"uid":143768,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"6aad6992fc91c5b03dbac2d735465598355c6744","tid":780771,"uid":169992,"like":11,"dislike":26,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T11:59:23.000Z","msg":"唔講以為佢揸車撞死咗人<br />\n唔明有嘜好鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T12:00:04.000Z","msg":"司機犯法"},{"pid":"4b2d1b04b14bfdc34063c19509cd6f6499de5896","tid":780771,"uid":49974,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T12:00:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔講以為佢揸車撞死咗人<br />\n唔明有嘜好鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啫係飲咗酒渣車冇撞死人都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e21a8f9e2f5da40f80a93b2272f3c39a0e56ef7","tid":780771,"uid":1703,"like":5,"disli